               <p>THOMAS REILLY. I am an <rs id="t18170219-38-viclabel214" type="occupation">agent</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-38-victim339 t18170219-38-viclabel214"></join>, and live in Leadenhall-street. On the 22nd of January, about one o'clock in the afternoon, as I was going along Cheapside, I thought I felt somebody at my pocket; I put my hand to it, and found my handkerchief safe. When I got to the middle of the <placeName id="t18170219-38-crimeloc215">Poultry</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18170219-38-crimeloc215" type="placeName" value="Poultry"></interp>
